In addition to the Haskell platform, the following Debian Packages required:

libghc-cmdargs-dev, libghc-mtl-dev, libghc-readline-dev, libghc-regex-base-dev, libghc-regex-posix-dev, libghc-split-dev, libghc-stm-dev, libghc-transformers-dev, libghc6-regex-base-dev, libghc6-regex-posix-dev, libghc6-split-dev, libghc6-stm-dev         

